{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, nobody was scared at the moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that's a thing that you did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at this moment, in the beginning, we hadn't heard that any group like this would be picked up, that they would bust into the homes or something like that and would pick it up.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, we-- I don't recall that we were scared or anything under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were happy and got together, and we have a lot of fun that way-- a lot of fun that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- well, first of all, the-- the fact that, naturally, that everybody disappeared, little by little, one after the other, but not yet right away at that moment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the next step would be important to consider the big change that took place on September 1, 1939, the date that Hitler marched into Poland at the start of World War II.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Immediately at that moment, all Jewish people who were working, no matter what they were doing, had to report to a building, like an unemployment center or something like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And immediately, we were not allowed to go back to our work jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were, in fact in my case-- not in every case.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people were sent home to report tomorrow again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In my case, I was immediately loaded onto a truck and taken to a work site, out of-- a little bit on the outskirt of the general Berlin, major Berlin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were put, in my case, on street work, to build streets and eventually parts of the Autobahn, the Germany highways.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we were immediately put into slavery work condition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, that means, number one, of course, we were allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
